metadata.name: Elulands Avatar #1
metadata.description: Elulands' mission is to revolutionize the anime PFP fan experience by providing unique and exclusive NFT-based artwork. We believe in starting small and building a tight-knit community. Our passion project is designed to be an exciting new collection that challenges the way we think about digital art ownership. Our NFTs offer a one-of-a-kind form of expression and serve as a reminder of true ownership within our ecosystem. For more information, visit elulands.com.
